title: Rosewill Green Series 530W 80 PLUS Certified Power Supply RG530-S12 Black
description: Today's premium computer parts require quality power, but that doesn't mean you have to spend a fortune. The Rosewill Green Series RG530-S12 530W power supply offers you everything you need to run contemporary PC components with ease. The RG530-S12 has all of the connections you need for today's hottest peripherals, including six 5pin SATA connectors for fast data transfer and two 6pin PCI-e connectors for the most powerful video cards. The RG530-S12 is ready for your SLI or CrossFire setups. The typical 4pin ATX12V/EPS12V connector is expandable to 8pins so you can use this power supply with your Core i5 or i7 Intel processor. The RG530-S12 will also look great in your case with its black coating housing. All of the connectors are sleeved in mesh for better cable management and routing for increased air flow. Experience the Rosewill quality and build your next PC with the RG530-S12 530W power supply today!
